value: Resident, all wetlands: S Sudan, SW Kenya - E Angola and south in E South Africa; NE Nigeria; W Angola.
Africa: inland wc, e, se Africa

forages in floating vegetation in stagnant water, e.g.lakes, pools, marshes;also in swamps, rivers & floodplains;in dry season in muddy edges of pools & small waterways;wet season inundated grassland & flooded rice fields

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
